headline: How proposed U.S. tariffs could disrupt PC supply chain
summary: Investing.com -- Proposed U.S. tariffs on imported PCs and components could cause significant price hikes, supply chain instability, and long-term shifts in manufacturing, according to Bank of America analysts.
